<item>
            <title>[LU-15522] liblnetconfig should not export readline</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15522</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If HAVE_LIBREADLINE is not defined then liblnetconfig.so will export readline(). This is a bug since it breaks readline if liblnetconfig is linked before libreadline.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="68514">LU-15522</key>
